{"id": 2216, "genre": 1000, "title": "除了商场，你觉得小朋友在城市里还应该有怎样的友好空间？", "description": "现在的城市都围绕交通和建筑建设，没有给孩子提供足够的空间，究竟一座儿童友好型城市应该是什么样的？（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 9854, "comment_count": 47, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180308162207OydDszfn0KWp1FSX.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-08T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3823, "title": "除了商场，你觉得小朋友在城市里还应该有怎样的友好空间？", "content": "除了商场，你觉得小朋友在城市里还应该有怎样的友好空间？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 269118, "content": "学校周边有足够安全的步行道和自行车道", "image": "img/option/option/20180308163604J0Slyf2pc5dL1keg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 269120, "content": "火车/地铁有儿童车厢，只提供给家长和孩子", "image": "img/option/option/20180308164239GWmB1ZChLR4VftEO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 269122, "content": "餐厅划分出儿童区域，有合适高度的桌椅", "image": "img/option/option/20180308164423kLSBwvKUcQbn3aiP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 269123, "content": "有家庭洗手间，供带女儿的父亲/带儿子的母亲使用", "image": "img/option/option/20180308165120bI0D87qXF1JN49xK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 269124, "content": "游乐园有足够多的儿童洗手池，孩子玩耍后需要常洗手", "image": "img/option/option/20180308165225sYFwjyJ3pl9cPUMi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 269125, "content": "自然博物馆/动物园等的标牌在标注英文的同时，也添加汉语拼音", "image": "img/option/option/201803081653435Gfbytvn6o3cQYIr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 269127, "content": "公园有儿童玩耍设施，而不是只有几个鸡肋的健身器", "image": "img/option/option/20180308165537XgkMvuWKQSqG37zE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 269130, "content": "影院有儿童厅，播放更适合孩子的电影", "image": "img/option/option/201803081657331ZBwSMQle72jGDYm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}